{"tid":1375144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"籌備全民無限期三罷","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T18:38:56.000Z","uid":173084,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"274ed92cc5c9f47f7e5f6011c532c581c94505b2","tid":1375144,"uid":173084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"事至如今，其實港共已經無彎轉<br />\n我地要支持勇武繼續做野，同時和理非都要幫手，無限期三罷就係我地最有力既手段<br />\n<br />\n個人建議：<br />\n1. 無限期罷工唔係個個一講就接受到，我地要一段較長既時間真係落區做文宣。612點解咁多人，都係因為前期工作做得好，有成一兩個月不同光譜既人不停宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n2. 假設用一個月做文宣（最好要有親身傾談，個個都做得，例如去茶記食個早餐都可以R老闆同食客），夾埋大學中學小學既開學時間，9月1號開始其實係一個唔錯既時機。<br />\n<br />\n3. 民陣幫下手please。<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推，文宣幫手做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e3c7d61f647e39f338e3194c9ff366d4a41f04","tid":1375144,"uid":173084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbd6e63e764e765301716ac134302c07c72426f3","tid":1375144,"uid":173084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51fdfa7ad52c35a39e40826e9f444d41ce423d10","tid":1375144,"uid":85097,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"今年9月1日星期日嚟<br />\n<br />\n2號星期一先開學日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f5d6adbe3eb75a02e6621b4b10b8a0862c5acd","tid":1375144,"uid":173084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51fdfa7ad52c35a39e40826e9f444d41ce423d10","tid":1375144,"uid":85097,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"今年9月1日星期日嚟<br />\n<br />\n2號星期一先開學日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:47:00.000Z","msg":"Ok 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdef975bbafae91ddbd84a0370c795c1ceac47b4","tid":1375144,"uid":173084,"like":